{"lemma":"راحَ","slug":"راحَ","root":"ر.#.ح","root_slug":"ر-_-ح","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-_-ح","pos":"V","pos_camel":"verb","paradigm":[{"role":"past_2ms","form":"رُحْتَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"past_2fs","form":"رُحْتِ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"2","gen":"f","num":"s"},{"role":"past_2md","form":"رُحْتُما","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"past_2mp","form":"رُحْتُم","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"past_2fp","form":"رُحْتُنَّ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"2","gen":"f","num":"p"},{"role":"past_3ms","form":"راحَ","in_corpus":true,"count":2,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"past_3fs","form":"راحَت","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"s"},{"role":"past_3md","form":"راحا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"past_3fd","form":"راحَتا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"d"},{"role":"past_3mp","form":"راحُوا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"past_3fp","form":"رُحْنَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"p"},{"role":"present_2ms","form":"تَرُح","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"present_2ms","form":"تَرُوح","in_corpus":true,"count":2,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"present_2fs","form":"تَرُوحِينَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"f","num":"s"},{"role":"present_2fs","form":"تَرُوحِي","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"f","num":"s"},{"role":"present_2md","form":"تَرُوحانِ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"present_2md","form":"تَرُوحا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"present_2mp","form":"تَرُوحُونَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"present_2mp","form":"تَرُوحُوا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"present_2fp","form":"تَرُحْنَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"f","num":"p"},{"role":"present_3ms","form":"يَرُح","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"present_3ms","form":"يَرُوح","in_corpus":true,"count":1,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"present_3fs","form":"تَرُح","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"s"},{"role":"present_3fs","form":"تَرُوح","in_corpus":true,"count":2,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"s"},{"role":"present_3md","form":"يَرُوحانِ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"present_3md","form":"يَرُوحا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"present_3fd","form":"تَرُوحانِ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"d"},{"role":"present_3fd","form":"تَرُوحا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"d"},{"role":"present_3mp","form":"يَرُوحُونَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"present_3mp","form":"يَرُوحُوا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"present_3fp","form":"يَرُحْنَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"p"},{"role":"past_1mp","form":"رُحْنا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"past_1ms","form":"رُحْتُ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"present_1ms","form":"أَرُوح","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"present_1mp","form":"نَرُوح","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"p"}],"frequency_in_corpus":7,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n16976","n16984"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%AD%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to go in the evening"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to go"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to go away"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to begin"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to come to the point where"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"wine","tags":["obsolete"],"examples":[{"text":"القبج بالفارسية هو الحجل عنه ومن كتاب أهرن وفي اللغة: القبج ذكر الحجل، قال الصنوبري\nيٰأخِي قُمْ فَقَدْ شَجَجْنا لَكَ الرَّاحَ … فَخُذْها مَشْجُوجَةً أيّ شَجّ\nقَطَعَ المَاءُ جِسْمَها قِطَعًا لَمْ … تَغْذِ أَمْثالَها مَناقِيرُ قَبْج","english":"Al-qabj is Persian for partridge ibidem [in ar-Rāzī’s Ḥāwī]. From ʾAhrun’s book and the lexicographers: It is the male partridge. Aṣ-Ṣanawbarīy said:\n O brother, get up! We have mixed wine for you.\n Take it in a mixed state in whichever fashion!\n The water has stripped down its substance into bits,\n of size smaller than partridge beaks eat."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of رَاحَة (rāḥa)","tags":["form-of","obsolete","plural"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root ر و ح (r w ḥ), from Proto-West Semitic *rawaḥ-."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n16976","headword_ar":"رَاحَ","root":"rwH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) sec. pers."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riHota","text_ar":"رِحْتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaraAHu","text_ar":"يَرَاحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riyHN","text_ar":"رِيحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) and aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaruwHu","text_ar":"يَرُوحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawoHN","text_ar":"رَوْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruw^uwHN","text_ar":"رُوُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a day)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was violently windy."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rAH","text_ar":"راح"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaruwHu","text_ar":"يَرُوحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruw^uwHN","text_ar":"رُوُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a day)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was one of good,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleasant, wind."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rAH","text_ar":"راح"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaraAHu","text_ar":"يَرَاحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawoHN","text_ar":"رَوْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, cool and pleasant"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by means of the wind"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (L.)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a house, or tent, the door being opened,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, aired by the wind;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was entered by the wind."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rAH Al$~ajaru","text_ar":"راح الشَّجَرُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The trees felt the wind."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHn, K.) [See also another meaning below.] ―         -b4-  [Hence, perhaps,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rAH","text_ar":"راح"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaraAHu","text_ar":"يَرَاحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAHN","text_ar":"رَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, brisk, lively, sprightly, active, agile, prompt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quick;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as though he felt the wind and was refreshed by it;] (L;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArtAH","text_ar":"ارتاح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, A, L, K:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAHN","text_ar":"رَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AirotiyaAHN","text_ar":"اِرْتِيَاحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signify the same: (S, L, K: [in the CK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlAirotiyAHi","text_ar":"الاِرْتِياحِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is erroneously put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlAirotiyaAHu","text_ar":"الاِرْتِيَاحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AisotarowaHa","text_ar":"اِسْتَرْوَحَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became light,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"active, and quick;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$am~ara","text_ar":"شَمَّرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rAH lil$~aYo'i","text_ar":"راح لِلشَّىْءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilaY Al$~aYo'i","text_ar":"اـِلَى الشَّىْءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArtAH","text_ar":"ارتاح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArtAH bihi","text_ar":"ارتاح بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, brisk, lively,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c, as above,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at the thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"betook himself with briskness, liveliness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and was rejoiced by it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, TA.) A poet says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"wa zaEamota A^an~aka laA taraAHu A_ilaY Aln~isaA"},{"kind":"text","text":"[(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And thou assertedst that thou dost not,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wilt not, betake thyself with briskness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to women, nor be rejoiced by them"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Lth, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rAH","text_ar":"راح"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liloA^amori","text_ar":"لِلْاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArtAH","text_ar":"ارتاح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He betook himself with briskness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affair;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was brisk,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to do it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rAH li*`lika AlA^amori","text_ar":"راح لِذٰلِكَ الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L,"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1178},{"kind":"text","text":"K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilayohi","text_ar":"اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaraAHN","text_ar":"يَرَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawaAHN","text_ar":"رَوَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruw^uwHN","text_ar":"رُوُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAHN","text_ar":"رَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riyaAHapN","text_ar":"رِيَاحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAHapN","text_ar":"رَاحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroyaHiy~apN","text_ar":"اَرْيَحِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L,) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He brightened in countenance at that thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, [there explained by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$oraqa lahu","text_ar":"اَشْرَقَ لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and this I regard as the right reading, rather than that which I find in the copies of the K, which is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$orafa lahu","text_ar":"اَشْرَفَ لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", perhaps meaning the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$orafa Ealayohi","text_ar":"اَشْرَفَ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he became acquainted with that thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"knew it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiT~alaEa Ealayohi","text_ar":"اِطَّلَعَ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":",])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and rejoiced in it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and was thereby affected with alacrity, cheerfulness, briskness, liveliness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sprightliness, disposing him to promptness in acts of kindness"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beneficence:"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of a generous man when he is asked to confer a gift; and sometimes, metaphorically, of dogs when called by their owner, and of other animals. (L.) [It is also said that]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawaAHN","text_ar":"رَوَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawaAHapN","text_ar":"رَوَاحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAHapN","text_ar":"رَاحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawoHapN","text_ar":"رَوْحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawiyHapN","text_ar":"رَوِيحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[all app. inf. ns. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAHa","text_ar":"رَاحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or some of them may be simple substs.,] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muraAyaHapN","text_ar":"مُرَايَحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as though inf. n. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAyaHa","text_ar":"رَايَحَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (L, K) signify (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"experiencing relief from grief"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sorrow, after suffering therefrom:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"experiencing the joy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"happiness, arising from certainty."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawoHN","text_ar":"رَوْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", below.]) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilaY Hadiyvihi","text_ar":"اـِلَى حَدِيثِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AisotarowaHotu","text_ar":"اِسْتَرْوَحْتُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I was affected with cheerfulness, liveliness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like, at his discourse,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"narration;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as seems to be indicated by the context in the place where it is mentioned: or perhaps,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he trusted to his discourse, and became quiet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"easy, in mind;"},{"kind":"text","text":"agreeably with an explanation of the verb which see below]: (A:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlY Hdyvh","text_ar":"الى حديثه"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstrAH","text_ar":"استراح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he inclined to his discourse."},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rAH lilomaEoruwfi","text_ar":"راح لِلْمَعْرُوفِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, L, K,) sec. pers."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riHota","text_ar":"رِحْتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaraAHu","text_ar":"يَرَاحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAHapN","text_ar":"رَاحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riyHN","text_ar":"رِيحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (L;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lh","text_ar":"له"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArtAH","text_ar":"ارتاح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A, L;) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was affected with alacrity, cheerfulness, briskness, liveliness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sprightliness, disposing him to promptness to do what was kind"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beneficent:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, S, L, K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he inclined to, and loved, kindness"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beneficence."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liln~adaY","text_ar":"لِلنَّدَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArtAH","text_ar":"ارتاح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was affected with alacrity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and so disposed to bounty"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"liberality"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nazalato","text_ar":"نَزَلَتْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@ll~`hu biraHomatihi faA^anoqa*ahu minohaA","text_ar":"ا@للّٰهُ بِرَحْمَتِهِ فَاَنْقَذَهُ مِنْهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bihi baliy~apN faA@rotaAHa","text_ar":"بِهِ بَلِيَّةٌ فَا@رْتَاحَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A trial,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an affliction, befell him, and God was active and prompt with his mercy, and delivered him from it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (T:) but ISd disapproves of thus speaking of God; and El-Fárisee says that it is an instance of the rudeness of speech characteristic of Arabs of the desert. (TA.) [Hence seems to have originated, as is app. implied in the TA, the assertion that] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlAirotiyaAHu","text_ar":"الاِرْتِيَاحُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being merciful:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@ll~`hu lahu biraHomatihi","text_ar":"ا@للّٰهُ لَهُ بِرَحْمَتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArtAH","text_ar":"ارتاح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God delivered him from trial,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affliction:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@ll~`hu lifulaAnK","text_ar":"ا@للّٰهُ لِفُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArtAH","text_ar":"ارتاح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God was merciful to such a one."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) One also says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rAHt yaduhu lika*aA","text_ar":"راحت يَدُهُ لِكَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bika*aA","text_ar":"بِكَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S L,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His hand was active, prompt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quick,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to do such a thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with such a thing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, TA;) as, for instance, with a sword, to strike with it. (L.) Hence the saying of the Prophet,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mano raAHa","text_ar":"مَنْ رَاحَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilaY AljumuEapi fiY Als~aAEapi AlA^uwlaY fakaA^an~amaA qad~ama badanapF","text_ar":"اـِلَى الجُمُعَةِ فِى السَّاعَةِ الاُولَى فَكَاَنَّمَا قَدَّمَ بَدَنَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Whosoever is brisk,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prompt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quick, in repairing to the Friday-prayers in the first hour, he is as though he offered a camel,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a cow"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bull, for sacrifice at Mekkeh"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (K, * TA:) the meaning is,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaf~a A_ilayohaA","text_ar":"خَفَّ اـِلَيْهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDaY","text_ar":"مَضَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) not the going in the latter part of the day. (K, * TA.) [See also what follows.] ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAHa","text_ar":"رَاحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaruwHu","text_ar":"يَرُوحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawaAHN","text_ar":"رَوَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"trw~H","text_ar":"تروّح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; both signify the same; (S, Msb, K, &c.;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gadaA","text_ar":"غَدَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;) said of a man, (TA,) and of a company of men, (K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they, went,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"journeyed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"worked,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"did a thing, in the evening,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the afternoon,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the declining of the sun from the meridian until night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IF, Msb, K, TA:) this is said to be the primary meaning: (TA:) but they also mean"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they, returned:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"journeyed, at any time:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, * TA:) [for]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~awaAHu","text_ar":"الرَّوَاحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is not, as some imagine it to be, only ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the going,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"journeying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the last,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"latter, part of the day;"},{"kind":"text","text":"but is used by the Arabs as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the going,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"journeying, at any time of the night or day;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alguduw~u","text_ar":"الغُدُوُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": so say Az and others: (Msb:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rAH","text_ar":"راح"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawaAHN","text_ar":"رَوَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he came,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went, after the declining of the sun from the meridian:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but is sometimes used as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he went"},{"kind":"text","text":"in an absolute sense: (Mgh:) and thus it means in the trad. commencing"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mano raAHa A_ilaY AljumuEapi","text_ar":"مَنْ رَاحَ اـِلَى الجُمُعَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[mentioned above, where a different explanation of the verb is given]: (Mgh, * Msb:) and [in like manner] one says to his companion or companions, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taraw~aHo","text_ar":"تَرَوَّحْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taraw~aHuwA","text_ar":"تَرَوَّحُوا"},{"kind":"text","text":"as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Go,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"journey:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) but"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAHati AlA_ibilu","text_ar":"رَاحَتِ الاـِبِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, L, K,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taruwHu","text_ar":"تَرُوحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taraAHu","text_ar":"تَرَاحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawaAHN","text_ar":"رَوَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAy^iHapN","text_ar":"رَايِحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AZ, L, K,) signifies only"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The camels returned in the evening,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"afternoon,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * Msb,) when their pastors drove or brought them back to their owners: so says Az. (Msb.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruHotu","text_ar":"رُحْتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilayohimo","text_ar":"اـِلَيْهِمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Einodahumo","text_ar":"عِنْدَهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawoHN","text_ar":"رَوْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawaAHN","text_ar":"رَوَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I went,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I came,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to them in the evening,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"afternoon;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at any time,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as appears from what has been said above;] and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruHotuhumo","text_ar":"رُحْتُهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawoHN","text_ar":"رَوْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raw~aHotuhumo","text_ar":"رَوَّحْتُهُمْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tarowiyHN","text_ar":"تَرْوِيحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taraw~aHotuhumo","text_ar":"تَرَوَّحْتُهُمْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K, TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anaA A^ugaAdiyhi wa A^uraAwiHuhu","text_ar":"اَنَا اُغَادِيهِ وَ اُرَاوِحُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I go,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"come, to him early in the morning, in the first part of the day,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between the time of the prayer of daybreak and sunrise, and I go,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"come, to him in the evening,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"afternoon,"},{"kind":"text","text":"app."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he doing the like to me"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A. [See also 6.]) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAHato Ealayohi A_ibiluhu","text_ar":"رَاحَتْ عَلَيْهِ اـِبِلُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ganamuhu","text_ar":"غَنَمُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAluhu","text_ar":"مَالُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His camels,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goats,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his cattle, returned to him after the declining of the sun from the meridian;"},{"kind":"text","text":"only at that time: and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArAHt","text_ar":"اراحت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"may perhaps be a dial. var. thereof: (L, TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rAHt biAlEa$iY~i EalaY A^aholihaA","text_ar":"راحت بِالعَشِىِّ عَلَى اَهْلِهَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they"},{"kind":"text","text":"(i. e. camels)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"returned from the place of pasture in the evening,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"afternoon, to their owners."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * Msb.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rAH Al$~ajaru","text_ar":"راح الشَّجَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, K,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yazaAHu","text_ar":"يَزَاحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, A;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"trw~H","text_ar":"تروّح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, A;) [said in the TA to be tropical, but not so in the A;]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The trees broke forth with leaves:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K:) or the former,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the trees broke forth with leaves before the winter, when the night became cold, without rain;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, TA;) and so the latter: (L:) or the latter,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the trees broke forth with leaves after the close of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sayof","text_ar":"صَيْف"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"summer"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlguSonu","text_ar":"الغُصْنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"trw~H","text_ar":"تروّح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The branch put forth leaves after other leaves had fallen from it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(R, TA.) [See another meaning of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rAH Al$jr","text_ar":"راح الشجر"},{"kind":"text","text":"near the beginning of this art.] ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rAH","text_ar":"راح"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaraAHu","text_ar":"يَرَاحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAHapN","text_ar":"رَاحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) said of a horse, [perhaps from the same verb as signifying “ he was, or became, brisk, lively, ” &c.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He became a stallion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fit to cover."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAHatohu Alr~iyHu","text_ar":"رَاحَتْهُ الرِّيحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taraAHu","text_ar":"تَرَاحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The wind smote it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, a thing; (L, K;) as, for instance, a tree, and said of a tempestuous wind. (L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riyHa","text_ar":"رِيحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of a pool of water left by a torrent,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was smitten"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blown upon"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by the wind."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K.) In like manner also it is said of other things. (TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riyHati Al$~ajarapu","text_ar":"رِيحَتِ الشَّجَرَةُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The tree was blown upon by the wind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was blown about,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shaken, by the wind, so that its leaves were made to fall:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had the dust scattered upon it by the wind."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riyHuwA","text_ar":"رِيحُوا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a people, or party,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"were smitten and destroyed by the wind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they entered upon"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a time of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wind;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) as also, in this latter sense, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^araAHuwA","text_ar":"اَرَاحُوا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arowaHuwA","text_ar":"اَرْوَحُوا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rAH Al$~aYo'a","text_ar":"راح الشَّىْءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A 'Obeyd, S, K,) first pers."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riHotu","text_ar":"رِحْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A 'Obeyd, S,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaraAHu","text_ar":"يَرَاحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A 'Obeyd, S, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yariyHu","text_ar":"يَرِيحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AA, S, K,) [inf. n., app., of the former"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawoHN","text_ar":"رَوْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and of the latter"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riyHN","text_ar":"رِيحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in the phrase of similar meaning following;] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^araAHahu","text_ar":"اَرَاحَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Ks, S, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arowaHahu","text_ar":"اَرْوَحَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (AZ, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He smelt the thing; perceived its smell,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"odour;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, &c.;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstrAHhu","text_ar":"استراحهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AisotarowaHahu","text_ar":"اِسْتَرْوَحَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Ham p. 228:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rAH Alr~iyHa","text_ar":"راح الرِّيحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaraAHu","text_ar":"يَرَاحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawoHN","text_ar":"رَوْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yariyHu","text_ar":"يَرِيحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riyHN","text_ar":"رِيحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^araAHahaA","text_ar":"اَرَاحَهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He smelt the odour."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) You say of an object of the chase, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^araAHaniY","text_ar":"اَرَاحَنِى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arowaHaniY","text_ar":"اَرْوَحَنِى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AZ, S, A,) inf. n. of the latter"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_irowaAHN","text_ar":"اـِرْوَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AZ, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He smelt me; perceived my smell,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"odour:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, S, A, TA:) and of the same, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArAH","text_ar":"اراح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arowaHa","text_ar":"اَرْوَحَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AisotarowaHa","text_ar":"اِسْتَرْوَحَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstrAH","text_ar":"استراح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He smelt a human being; perceived his smell,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"odour:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, K:) and the second of these four, (K, TA,) and the third and fourth, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he smelt gently, that he might perceive the odour of a thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) or the third and fourth of the same,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he smelt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perceived, odour:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) and these two, said of a stallion,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he perceived the smell of the female:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and of a beast of prey you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~iyHa","text_ar":"الرِّيحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arowaHa","text_ar":"اَرْوَحَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^araAHahaA","text_ar":"اَرَاحَهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstrAHhA","text_ar":"استراحها","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AisotarowaHahaA","text_ar":"اِسْتَرْوَحَهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he smelt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perceived, the odour;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and accord. to Lh, some say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAHahaA","text_ar":"رَاحَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but this is seldom used. (TA) [It is asserted (in Har p. 324) that ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstrAH","text_ar":"استراح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is only from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~aAHapu","text_ar":"الرَّاحَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but this assertion is of no weight against the authorities cited above.] It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mano qatala nafosFA muEaAhidapF lamo yaraHN raAy^iHapa Aljan~api","text_ar":"مَنْ قَتَلَ نَفْسًا مُعَاهِدَةً لَمْ يَرَحٌ رَايِحَةَ الجَنَّةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A 'Obeyd, S, Mgh, * Msb, *) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lm yariHo","text_ar":"لم يَرِحْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AA, S, Msb,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lm yuriHo","text_ar":"لم يُرِحْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Ks, S, Mgh, Msb,) i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He who slays a person with whom he is on terms of"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1179},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"peace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(or, as in' the TA,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muw^ominFA","text_ar":"مُوْمِنًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a believer,"},{"kind":"text","text":")]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he will not perceive the odour of Paradise:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb:) As says, I know not whether it be from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riHotu","text_ar":"رِحْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^araHotu","text_ar":"اَرَحْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"minohu TiybFA","text_ar":"مِنْهُ طِيبًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arowaHotu","text_ar":"اَرْوَحْتُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I perceived from him"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man, S)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a sweet odour."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A.) ―         -b3-  [And hence, app.,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rAH minoka maEoruwfFA","text_ar":"راح مِنْكَ مَعْرُوفًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArAHhu","text_ar":"اراحهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He obtained from thee a favour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"benefit."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawiHa","text_ar":"رَوِحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yarowaHu","text_ar":"يَرْوَحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawaHN","text_ar":"رَوَحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had the quality termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawaHN","text_ar":"رَوَحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [explained below, i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"width in the space between the thighs"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"legs;"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.; or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a spreading in the fore part of each foot."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawiHato qadamuhu","text_ar":"رَوِحَتْ قَدَمُهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His foot had the quality so termed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","TA","A","L","As","T","IF","Mgh","AZ","AA","Ks"]},{"entry_id":"n16984","headword_ar":"رَاحٌ","root":"rwH","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Windy;"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a day: (TA:) or, so applied,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"violently-windy;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAy^iHN","text_ar":"رَايِحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is the original form, (Msb,) or may be so: (TA:) fem. of the former with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":", applied to a night ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolapN","text_ar":"لَيْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"). (A, TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ray~iHN","text_ar":"رَيِّحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*ihi layolapN raAHapN lilomakoruwbi fiyhaA raAHapN","text_ar":"هٰذِهِ لَيْلَةٌ رَاحَةٌ لِلْمَكْرُوبِ فِيهَا رَاحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is a windy night: the oppressed in mind has rest therein"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.)       -A2-  It is also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AirotiyaAHN","text_ar":"اِرْتِيَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, L, K. [See 1, near the beginning of the paragraph.]) ―         -b2-  And [hence,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Wine;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, * K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rayaAHN","text_ar":"رَيَاحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) so called because the drinker thereof becomes brisk, lively, or sprightly; or, accord. to IHsh, because he becomes affected with briskness, liveliness, or sprightliness, disposing him to generous actions: in the L, [which mentions these two words in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ryH","text_ar":"ريح"},{"kind":"text","text":",] the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A","text_ar":"ا"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the former word is said to be substituted for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and hence the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the latter if such be the case]. (TA.)       -A3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAHapN","text_ar":"رَاحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in four places."}],"source_refs":["TA","Msb","S","K"]}]}}